result.notes: CQI is a workbench used to record  details of enquiries made into Income Tax Self Assessment and Corporation Tax Self Assessment returns.  It does not include enquiries by the HMRC's Large Business Service (LBS), Special Investigations (SI) or Employer Compliance Reviews. Updated: weekly. Data coverage: Latest 7 years (rolling)

organization.description:
What we do

We are the UK’s tax authority. We are responsible for making sure that the money is available to fund the UK’s public services and for helping families and individuals with targeted financial support.

HMRC is a non-ministerial department, supported by 2 agencies and public bodies.
